## Test: david_003 — Both client ($1,957.50) and DOL ($1,957.50) adjusted income above A1E 2026 standard ($1,845) — deny

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestDavid003:
  result scope Eligibility.EligibilityDecision

scope TestDavid003:
  definition result.client_data equals Eligibility.ClientData {
    -- gross_earned_income: $4,000
    -- federal_exclusions: $0
    -- eitc_exclusion: $0
    -- irregular_earned_income: $0
    -- student_earned_income: $0
    -- student_monthly_limit: $0
    -- non_needs_based_unearned_remainder: $20
    -- impairment_work_expenses: $0
    -- blind_work_expenses: $0
    -- self_support_exclusion: $0
    -- household_type: A1E
    -- benefit_year: 2026
  }
  definition result.d_o_l_record equals Eligibility.DOLRecord {
    -- dol_earned_income_available: true
    -- dol_quarterly_earnings: $12,000
    -- gross_earned_income: $4,000
    -- federal_exclusions: $0
    -- eitc_exclusion: $0
    -- irregular_earned_income: $0
    -- student_earned_income: $0
    -- student_monthly_limit: $0
    -- non_needs_based_unearned_remainder: $20
    -- impairment_work_expenses: $0
    -- blind_work_expenses: $0
    -- self_support_exclusion: $0
  }
  assertion (result.eligible = Deny)
  assertion (result.reasons = [ IncomeExceedsStandardBoth ])
```

## Test: david_004 — B1E, complex exclusion chain (federal/EITC/infrequent/student/blind work/self-support): client $2,337.50 and DOL $2,587.50 both above standard — deny

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestDavid004:
  result scope Eligibility.EligibilityDecision

scope TestDavid004:
  definition result.client_data equals Eligibility.ClientData {
    -- gross_earned_income: $6,000
    -- federal_exclusions: $50
    -- eitc_exclusion: $500
    -- irregular_earned_income: $10
    -- student_earned_income: $600
    -- student_monthly_limit: $2,410
    -- non_needs_based_unearned_remainder: $20
    -- impairment_work_expenses: $0
    -- blind_work_expenses: $20
    -- self_support_exclusion: $20
    -- household_type: B1E
    -- benefit_year: 2026
  }
  definition result.d_o_l_record equals Eligibility.DOLRecord {
    -- dol_earned_income_available: true
    -- dol_quarterly_earnings: $19,500
    -- gross_earned_income: $6,500
    -- federal_exclusions: $50
    -- eitc_exclusion: $500
    -- irregular_earned_income: $10
    -- student_earned_income: $600
    -- student_monthly_limit: $2,410
    -- non_needs_based_unearned_remainder: $20
    -- impairment_work_expenses: $0
    -- blind_work_expenses: $20
    -- self_support_exclusion: $20
  }
  assertion (result.eligible = Deny)
  assertion (result.reasons = [ IncomeExceedsStandardBoth ])
```

## Test: david_005 — B1E: blind work expenses ($300) and self-support plan ($150) fully eliminate adjusted income — client and DOL both $0 — approve

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestDavid005:
  result scope Eligibility.EligibilityDecision

scope TestDavid005:
  definition result.client_data equals Eligibility.ClientData {
    -- gross_earned_income: $500
    -- federal_exclusions: $0
    -- eitc_exclusion: $0
    -- irregular_earned_income: $0
    -- student_earned_income: $0
    -- student_monthly_limit: $0
    -- non_needs_based_unearned_remainder: $20
    -- impairment_work_expenses: $0
    -- blind_work_expenses: $300
    -- self_support_exclusion: $150
    -- household_type: B1E
    -- benefit_year: 2026
  }
  definition result.d_o_l_record equals Eligibility.DOLRecord {
    -- dol_earned_income_available: true
    -- dol_quarterly_earnings: $1,500
    -- gross_earned_income: $500
    -- federal_exclusions: $0
    -- eitc_exclusion: $0
    -- irregular_earned_income: $0
    -- student_earned_income: $0
    -- student_monthly_limit: $0
    -- non_needs_based_unearned_remainder: $20
    -- impairment_work_expenses: $0
    -- blind_work_expenses: $300
    -- self_support_exclusion: $150
  }
  assertion (result.eligible = Approve)
  assertion (result.reasons = [])
```

